KEN><TOKEN sid="p33_s2486" id="p33_w38" href="http://mindsc.ape.jp/klel/yui.cgi?xik=enxik&amp;axn=axnyui&amp;ism=ismyui&amp;rein=j&amp;ziko=ilm" font-name="ipa¾©" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="242.35" y="233.09" base="241.01" width="49.689" height="9">なのでむしろ</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p33_s2487" id="p33_w39" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="293.35" y="234.863" base="241.01" width="3.501" height="8.1">s</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p33_s2488" id="p33_w40" font-name="ipa¾©" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="298.27" y="233.09" base="241.01" width="74.163" height="9">で転写したいが、そ</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="57.96" height="9" id="p33_t13" x="48.264" y="250.13"><TOKEN sid="p33_s2489" id="p33_w41" font-name="ipa¾©" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="48.264" y="250.13" base="258.05" width="57.96" height="9">うもいくまい。</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="319.996" height="9.873" id="p33_t14" x="56.424" y="267.05"><TOKEN sid="p33_s2492" id="p33_w42" font-name="ipa¾©" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="56.424" y="267.05" base="274.97" width="228.969" height="9">よく見るとこの字はすべて一筆書きだ。ゕルフゔベットでさえ</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p33_s2493" id="p33_w43" font-name="times new roman" symbolic="yes" fixed-width="yes" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="286.75" y="268.823" base="274.97" width="4.5" height="8.1">2</TOKEN><TOKEN sid="p33_s2494" id="p33_w44" font-name="ipa¾©" bold="no" italic="no" font-size="9" font-color="#000000" rotation="0" angle="0" x="292.87" y="267.05" base="274.97" width="83.55" height="9">画のものがあるのに、</TOKEN></TEXT><TEXT width="147.479" height="9.873" id="p33_t15" x="48.264" y="284.11"><TOKEN sid="p33_s2495" id="p33_w45" font-name="ipa¾©" bold="no" italic=